name: Universe #297
description: Universe #297 - The lights of Sogantu hadn't shone through the cracks for a long time after surfaces of it's worlds dried after a close call with a hot nebula which threatened it's existence. Now it tried to rip through the dried surface but it's core was getting weaker every passing moment. 297 saw and rushed to it's help. Now it helps with it's own energy as 297 starts shining once more.
